                                How Petopia works for Pet Care Providers </h3>

                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    <b>Register:</b><br />
                                    Register for an account with us, and designate yourself
                                    as a "Pet Care Provider".
                                    <br /><br /><br />
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <b>Your Profile -- and your Pet(s):</b><br />
                                    Then you'll get to fill in the profile details for you
                                    and your Pet(s).
                                    <br /><br />
