                                    "card(s)" on your own profile -- click a card to go to
                                    that Pet's full profile!
                                    <br /><br />
                                    You can come back and edit or update your details any
                                    time you like -- add badges, pets, and any new experience
                                    &amp; qualifications you get.
                                    <br /><br /><br />
                                </li>
