                                    The account information you provivde does not and will
                                    not appear on your profile, so no worries!
                                    <br /><br />
                                    When you contract with a Pet Owner to care for their pet,
                                    we will provide them with the contact information you
                                    supplied so they know how to reach you and that you are
                                    a real person.
                                    <br /><br /><br />
                                </li>
