                                    your profile so Pet Owners can see at a glance the pets
                                    you work with!
                                    <br /><br /><br />
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <b>Providing Pet Care:</b><br />
                                    Once you have your profile details filled out, you'll be
                                    taken to your profile page to review it.
                                    <br /><br />
                                    But, before you can "go live" and accept Pet Care
                                    assignments..... you'll have to (successfully!) complete
                                    and pass a background check.  This will show on your
                                    profile so that Pet Owners know you're "vetted" and
                                    trust-worthy to care for their special pets in their
                                    home!
                                    <br /><br />
                                    Once everything has cleared, you'll be good to go.
                                    Just indicate on your schedule\calendar, the days and
                                    times you're available, so Pet Owners can see it.  Then
                                    just wait to be matched up with Pets and their Owners!
                                    <br /><br />
                                    When a Pet Owner contacts you via private message from
                                    within Petopia, the two of you can get to know each other
                                    a little and settle any outstanding details -- and you'll
                                    get the instructions you'll need in order to complete
                                    your pet care assignment.
                                    <br /><br /><br />
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <b>Scheduling &amp; Calendars:</b> <br />
                                    When you initially set up your profile, mark on your
                                    schedule\calendar the days &amp; times you're
                                    available to provide Pet Care.
                                    <br /><br />
                                    You can update your availability at any time, and your
                                    changes will be reflected in real time.
                                    <br /><br />
                                    Your calendar will be visible on your profile for Pet
                                    Owners to see when you're open.  This will just add one
                                    more layer of "easy" for Pet Owners to know if you're
                                    the one for them!
                                    <br /><br />
                                    Pet Owners can click on a block of time to reserve that
                                    spot for you to care for their Pet.
                                    <br /><br /><br />
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <b>Check-Ins &amp; End-of-Visit Notes:</b> <br />
                                    Let your Pet Owner know what's up with their Pet!
                                    <br /><br />
                                    Check-In when you arrive and leave, and any other points
                                    as arranged between you and your Pet Owner -- when the
                                    Pet got it's meds, dinner, walk or play-time, let in/out,
                                    picked up or dropped off -- whatever care you're doing --
                                    and Petopia will send the Pet Owner Check-In alerts in
                                    real time!
                                    <br /><br />
                                    At the end of each Pet Care visit, be sure to fill in
                                    any notes about the visit -- how things went and anything
                                    the Pet Owner may need or want to know about their
                                    Pet(s) to know they were happy &amp; well-cared-for.
                                    <br /><br />
                                    Your Check-Ins &amp; End-of-Visit Notes will become part
                                    of a Pet's "Permanent Care Record" with Petopia that the
                                    Pet Owner and you or other Pet Care Providers can review
                                    at any time.
                                    <br /><br />
                                    This way -- no matter who takes care of a given Pet --
                                    they'll always have access to helpful notes so they can
                                    take the best care of the Pet that they can.
                                    <br /><br />
                                    Remember that following good Check-In practices will
                                    help to improve your ratings, so that you are more
                                    likely to get more Pet Care work!
                                    <br /><br /><br />
                                </li>
                                
                                <li>
