                                    providing the care agreed to with TLC as if it's your own
                                    pet, and leaving good Check-Ins and after-visit notes.
                                    <br /><br /><br />
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <b>Getting Paid for your Pet Care:</b> <br />
