                                    Owners know up-front how much to expect to pay.  They
                                    are free to tip for above-and-beyond service!
                                    <br /><br />
                                    Once each Pet Care assignment is complete, the Pet Owner
                                    will be sent an invoice, and payments will be handled
                                    from inside the Petopia app, and go directly to you!
                                    <br /><br />
                                    Your payment records will be available from your
                                    Petopia account.
                                    <br /><br /><br />
                                </li>
                                
                                <!--======================================================-->
                            </ul>

